What is Cashtagram?

Cashtagram is an expense tracking app that helps you manage your finances by keeping track of your expenses. With Cashtagram, you can easily add expenses, categorize them, and view detailed overviews of your spending habits.

Adding an Expense

To add an expense, click on the "Add Expense" button. You will be prompted to enter the amount, select a category, and add a description for the expense.

Expense Overview

Cashtagram provides you with a detailed overview of your expenses. You can view your expenses in a chart format, with options to view monthly, daily, and yearly expenses.

Get Started

To get started with Cashtagram, simply sign up for an account and start tracking your expenses today!
